WEBVTT

00:02.031 --> 00:04.948
When you're a kid, that's lots of fun to be had.

00:07.087 --> 00:09.059
Do you like to have a great time?

00:10.439 --> 00:14.069
Sometimes, kids can do silly things to make you sad.

00:17.770 --> 00:18.865
Oh, no!

00:19.150 --> 00:20.488
Someone took Cliff!

00:22.425 --> 00:27.228
But no matter how much you might get angry,...

00:30.026 --> 00:31.491
Wow!

00:33.261 --> 00:35.355
Can you get my doggy back, please?

00:40.537 --> 00:45.104
...it's always good to give that kid a chance to say sorry.

00:52.689 --> 00:56.382
Be a giant, say sorry.

